summary: Today it’s been four years since I met David, Olivia and Jodie in Broadchurch West Bay! It was the day when the cast of series 2...
caption: Today it’s been four years since I met David, Olivia and Jodie in Broadchurch West Bay! It was the day when the cast of series 2 was taking photos on the beach amongst the bluebells. I hadn’t expected to meet them, I just was there to see the location. But of course when I saw them I decided that I wouldn’t forgive myself if I didn’t try to talk to DT. :D And I did. Four years have passed and I still remember every single word of that short conversation, and how kind he was, and his eyes above the sunglasses and how he immediately shook my hand when I aproached. ;) Olivia was nice and quiet and smiling, and I tried to talk to both of them, for it would have been rude to address to David only. ;) Oh, and I also had talked to Jodie Whittaker before I met these two, and she was extremely modest, she even said, “I’ll write who I played… [in case you don’t remember]” And I was like “I know who you played, you were amazing!” So, it’s funny now, ‘cos I’d met The Doctor before she became the Doctor :D

summary: Question for Catherine Tate & John Barrowman: Is David Tennant a good kisser? from DragonCon - September 2018 Other favorite...
caption:
Question for Catherine Tate & John Barrowman: Is David Tennant a good kisser?
from DragonCon - September 2018

Other favorite parts of this segment:  
- Catherine being surprised/disbelieving (protective?) about John having kissed David (”Why have you kissed him?”)
- Catherine’s response of “That must have been before me because he’d never have gone on to you after me,“ after John confirmed that he really had kissed David
